機外型靚d之外 都係覺得iphone 易用好多 只係講三叔個英文keyboard auto correct已經用撚到炆</blockquote><br />\n我覺得支spen最實用，其他都係一般智能手機嘢，分別不大。</blockquote><br />\n個live message用黎溝女真係一流"},{"pid":"3624c029d442713c98c743f31b0fb73cb815c35a","tid":463490,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"買哂"},{"pid":"cf0b73eb82d5dbfddad760582e95907bce6e56ee","tid":463490,"uid":43227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用左幾代iphone岩岩轉會note8 除左部機外型靚d之外 都係覺得iphone 易用好多 只係講三叔個英文keyboard auto correct已經用撚到炆</blockquote><br />\n我覺得支spen最實用，其他都係一般智能手機嘢，分別不大。</blockquote><br />\n個live message用黎溝女真係一流</blockquote><br />\n係唔錯嘅，雖則ios已有類似功能，叫digital touch。但我覺得畫呢類用筆係會靚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c763cd7581c05bc4794a9eb4c57a749ec35d00","tid":463490,"uid":70060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f2bb4ce1199d474b3d707950873d8eab657a1cd","tid":463490,"uid":8718,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"我用緊7plus都心思思想轉note8/u11+<br />\n最大糾結位係an機啲emoji真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828455712bc52469fffab537bf2e61a546cc5f1c","tid":463490,"uid":19218,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"主機:note8<br />\n副機:6s<br />\n<br />\n明顯新機note8 又快又爽<br />\n<br />\n得閒就禁支筆出黎玩下。<br />\n<br />\n工作上,note8 可以幫到手,拉支筆出黎就可以寫筆記非常方便。<br />\n<br />\n缺點太長,難以單手玩。"},{"pid":"dcd6a59cc82a0f336acfb7d99e6e6107e979a27e","tid":463490,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"成班打手水人買note8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46cfe17f1f2e05